We generalized the normalized cut algorithm, implemented by optimizing normalized association as objective function, to overcome the imaging noise for obtaining reliable brain parcellation by integrating prior and spatial information into the objective function defined in Eq. (3). The parameters \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
