Since there has been a large quantity of brain’s structural/functional knowledge, we adopted the prior knowledge as supervision information in a semi-supervised clustering method within a graph partitioning framework for obtaining reliable brain parcellation with improved functional homogeneity shown in Fig. 547. There are two parameters \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
