				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\varvec{Nassoc}}_{{\varvec{k}}}$$\end{document}Nassock47,52,74,75, which has been detailedly described in our preliminary study45.

